# =============================================================================
# SAFE FILES THAT SHOULD BE COMMITTED (examples / templates)
# =============================================================================
# .env.example          ← OK and encouraged (contains only placeholders)
# .env.template         ← OK
# QUICKSTART.md         ← must only ever contain ${VAR} or "0xYour..." placeholders
# README.md             ← same rule
#
# When adding new documentation or examples:
#   - ALWAYS use placeholders: ${PK}, ${CLOB_API_KEY}, 0xYourPrivateKeyHere, ...
#   - NEVER paste a real private key, CLOB secret, or API key.
# =============================================================================
